<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>LaporPak - Pilih Akses</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
        }
        h1 { color: #333; }
        .container {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .card {
            padding: 20px 40px;
            background: #007bff;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .card:hover { background: #0056b3; transform: translateY(-5px); }
        .admin { background: #28a745; }
        .admin:hover { background: #218838; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>Selamat Datang di LaporPak</h1>
    <p>Pilih menu akses di bawah ini:</p>

    <div class="container">
        <a href="./petugas/" class="card">Aplikasi Petugas</a>
        <a href="./admin/" class="card">Halaman Admin</a>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
